window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Questions and answers abound in the </b><b><i>Rebel Star</i></b></p> <p>Weary and tired from playing galactic bounty hunter and assassin, John and his crew of intrepid human survivors find themselves in Spaks after their latest escapade bring more heat than ever. In the outcast station of rebels and pirates, John is caught up in galactic politics once again.&nbsp;</p> <p>As trouble approaches on the hyperdrive engines of his many enemies, John finds answers to the System Quest and even more questions in the Rebel Station.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Rebel Star</i> is book eight of the System Apocalypse, a LitRPG apocalypse series that combines modern-day life, science fiction, and fantasy elements along with game mechanics.</p>"; 
